<expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>schr<ex>iben</ex></expan> hat von
                            <expan>Wilh<ex>elm</ex></expan> von Lysperg, <add>des
                                    <expan>jüng<ex>er</ex>n</expan></add>, wegen etc., also send wir
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>fürstenlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> gnaden hirynne
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>slossen</expan> abschrift czweyer brief, wie sich
                                <expan>vorczeite<ex>n</ex></expan> die von Lysperg gen
                                <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> lantfride
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und verpunden
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. <expan>Dan<ex>n</ex></expan> wo etc.
